ld events, concerts and other local [[soccer|football]] teams. It has a capacity of 35,000 and the first phase of the project was completed in 2004 after more than 10 years. The latter phases will be completed in a few years time and will increase the stadiums capacity.\n\n==Notable matches==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n!Date\n!Team #1\n!Res.\n!Team #2\n!Competition\n!Attendance\n!Remarks\n|-\n|24 December 2004<ref>http://www.persianleague.com/history.html?view=teamfixtures&id=14&team=56&displayresults=yes&badges_ondisplay=yes</ref>||[[F.C. Aboomoslem|Abumoslem]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\u20130||[[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]]||[[IPL 2004/05]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|35,000||First home game and a victory over Persepolis\n|-\n|19 January 2006<ref>http://www.iplstats.com/website05-06/Week19/ABU_EST_19.htm</ref>||[[F.C. Aboomoslem|Abumoslem]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\u20130||[[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]]||[[2005\u201306 Iran Pro League]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|30,000||Victory over Esteghlal\n|-\n|9 September 2006<ref>http://www.iplstats.com/website06-07/Week01/ABU_PER_01.htm</ref>||[[F.C. Aboomoslem|Abumoslem]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\u20132||[[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]]||[[2006\u201307 Iran Pro League]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|32,000||Victory over Persepolis\n|-\n|18 April 2008<ref>http://www.iplstats.com/website07-08/Week28/ABU_EST_28.htm</ref>||[[F.C. Aboomoslem|Abumoslem]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\u20130||[[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]]||[[2007\u201308 Iran Pro League]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|35,000||Victory over Esteghlal\n|-\n|12 September 2008<ref>http://www.iplstats.com/website08-09/Week06/ABU_ZOB_06.htm</ref>||[[F.C. Aboomoslem|Abumoslem]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\u20130||[[Zob Ahan F.C.|Zobahan]]||[[2008\u201309 Iran Pro League]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"|7,000|| Defeated Zob Ahan 4-0\n|-\n|8 October 2008<ref>http://www.iplstats.com/website08-09/Week10/ABU_PER_10.htm</