ine.com/news/38/airlineroute/287613/tui-airways-resumes-sharm-el-sheikh-service-from-feb-2020/|work=routesonline.com|date=19 November 2019}}</ref> [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Agadir\u2013Al Massira Airport|Agadir]], [[Alicante Airport|Alicante]], [[Almer\u00eda Airport|Almeria]] (begins 3 May 2020),<ref name=\"TUI.uk\"/> [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]], [[Grantley Adams International Airport|Barbados]], [[Milas-Bodrum Airport|Bodrum]], [[Burgas Airport|Burgas]], [[Canc\u00fan International Airport|Canc\u00fan]], [[Chania International Airport|Chania]], [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]], [[Dalaman Airport|Dalaman]], [[Dubrovnik Airport|Dubrovnik]], [[Enfidha\u2013Hammamet International Airport|Enfidha]] (resumes 4 May 2020),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bristolpost.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/tui-announces-new-flight-route-2844740|title=TUI announces new flight route to Enfidha from Bristol Airport for summer 2020|date=8 May 2019|website=bristolpost.co.uk|access-date=26 May 2019}}</ref> [[Faro Airport|Faro]], [[Fuerteventura Airport|Fuerteventura]], [[Girona\u2013Costa Brava Airport|Girona]], [[Heraklion International Airport|Heraklion]], [[Ibiza Airport|Ibiza]], [[\u0130zmir Adnan Menderes Airport|Izmir]] (begins 2 May 2020),<ref name=\"TUI.uk\"/> [[Kephalonia International Airport|Kefalonia]], [[Kittil\u00e4 Airport|Kittil\u00e4]], [[Kos International Airport|Kos]], [[Larnaca International Airport|Larnaca]], [[Malta International Airport|Malta]], [[Marrakesh Menara Airport|Marrakesh]], [[Menorca Airport|Menorca]], [[Naples International Airport|Naples]], [[Orlando Sanford International Airport|Orlando/Sanford]], [[Palma de Mallorca Airport|Palma de Mallorca]], [[Pula Airport|Pula]], [[Reus Airport|Reus]], [[Keflav\u00edk International Airport|Reykjav\u00edk\u2013Keflav\u00edk]], [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]], [[Santorini (Thira) International Airport|Santorini]], [[Skiathos International Airport|Skiathos]], [[Thessaloniki Airport|Thessaloniki]], [[Verona Villafranca Airport|Verona]], [[Zakynthos International Airport|Zakynthos]] <br> \n<!-- -->\n| [[Wizz Air]] | [[Katowice Airport|Katowice]]\n<!-- -->\n}}\n\n==Statistics==\n===Passengers and movements===\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n|-\n!| !! Number of<br>passengers<ref group=note>Number of passengers including domestic, international and transit.</ref> !! style=\"width:125px\"| Number of<br>movements<ref group=note>Number of movements represents total takeoffs and landings during that year.</ref> !! Bristol Airport passenger totals<br>1997\u20132018 (millions)\n|-\n!1997\n|1,614,837 || 59,547 || bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" rowspan=\"21\" | <timeline>\nImageSize = width:auto height:250 barincrement:29\nPlotArea = left:30 bottom:15 top:10 right:15\nAlignBars = justify\nPeriod = from:0 till:9\nTimeAxis = orientation:vertical\n\nColors =\n id:gray value:gray(0.5)\n id:line1 value:gray(0.9)\n id:line2 value:gray(0.7)\n\nScaleMajor = start:0 increment:1 gridcolor:line2\nScaleMinor = start:0 increment:1 gridcolor:line1\n\nPlotData=\n color:blue width:22\n bar:1997 from:start till:1.614\n bar:1998 from:start till:1.838\n bar:1999 from:start till:1.993\n bar:2000 from:start till:2.146\n bar:2001 from:start till:2.694\n bar:2002 from:start till:3.446\n bar:2003 from:start till:3.915\n bar:2004 from:start till:4.647\n bar:2005 from:start till:5.254\n bar:2006 from:start till:5.758\n bar:2007 from:start till:5.927\n bar:2008 from:start till:6.267\n bar:2009 from:start till:5.643\n bar:2010 from:start till:5.748\n bar:2011 from:start till:5.781\n bar:2012 from:start till:5.926\n bar:2013 from:start till:6.132\n bar:2014 from:start till:6.340\n bar:2015 from:start till:6.787\n bar:2016 from:start till:7.611\n bar:2017 from:start till:8.239\n color:darkblue\n bar:2018 from:start till:8.700</timeline>\n|-\n!1998\n|1,838,219 || 61,582\n|-\n!1999\n|1,993,331 || 62,072\n|-\n!2000\n|2,141,525 || 63,252\n|-\n!2001\n|2,694,464 || 69,854\n|-\