o]], [[Fuerteventura Airport|Fuerteventura]], [[Madeira Airport|Funchal]], [[Geneva International Airport|Geneva]], [[Gibraltar Airport|Gibraltar]], [[Glasgow Airport|Glasgow]], [[Hurghada International Airport|Hurghada]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=easyJet schedules new routes in W19 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/285399/easyjet-schedules-new-routes-in-w19/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=16 July 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716035101/https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/285399/easyjet-schedules-new-routes-in-w19/ |archive-date=16 July 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref> [[Inverness Airport|Inverness]], [[Isle of Man Airport|Isle of Man]], [[John Paul II International Airport Krak\u00f3w-Balice|Krak\u00f3w]], [[Lanzarote Airport|Lanzarote]], [[Larnaca International Airport|Larnaca]],<ref name=\"easyjet.com\">{{cite web|url=https://www.easyjet.com/en/book/our-new-routes?link_megadrop|title=New routes from the UK - easyJet|website=www.easyjet.com|access-date=18 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712120447/https://www.easyjet.com/en/book/our-new-routes?link_megadrop|archive-date=12 July 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Lisbon Portela Airport|Lisbon]], [[Lyon-Saint Exup\u00e9ry Airport|Lyon]], [[Madrid-Barajas Airport|Madrid]], [[M\u00e1laga Airport|M\u00e1laga]], [[Malpensa Airport|Milan\u2013Malpensa]], [[Regi\u00f3n de Murcia International Airport|Murcia]], [[Naples Airport|Naples]], [[Newcastle International Airport|Newcastle upon Tyne]], [[Palma de Mallorca Airport|Palma de Mallorca]], [[Paphos International Airport|Paphos]], [[Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]], [[Paris Orly Airport|Paris\u2013Orly]],<ref>https://www.easyjet.com/en/book/our-new-routes</ref> [[Pisa International Airport|Pisa]], [[Francisco de S\u00e1 Carneiro Airport|Porto]], [[Prague Ruzyne Airport|Prague]], [[Rome\u2013Fiumicino]], [[San Pablo Airport|Seville]], [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]], [[Toulouse-Blagnac Airport|Toulouse]], [[Venice Marco Polo Airport|Venice]], [[Vienna International Airport|Vienna]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]] (begins 3 May 2020),<ref>https://www.easyjet.com/en/book/our-new-routes</ref> [[Biarritz Airport|Biarritz]], [[Milas-Bodrum Airport|Bodrum]], [[Brindisi Airport|Brindisi]], [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]], [[Dalaman Airport|Dalaman]], [[Dubrovnik Airport|Dubrovnik]], [[Gran Canaria Airport|Gran Canaria]], [[Grenoble-Is\u00e8re Airport|Grenoble]], [[Heraklion International Airport|Heraklion]], [[Ibiza Airport|Ibiza]], [[Innsbruck Airport|Innsbruck]], [[Cephalonia International Airport|Kefalonia]], [[Kos Airport|Kos]] (begins 4 May 2020), [[La Rochelle \u2013 \u00cele de R\u00e9 Airport|La Rochelle]], [[Marseille Provence Airport|Marseille]], [[Menorca Airport|Menorca]], [[Montpellier\u2013M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e Airport|Montpellier]], [[Nantes Airport|Nantes]], [[Nice C\u00f4te d'Azur Airport|Nice]], [[Olbia Costa Smeralda Airport|Olbia]], [[Aktion National Airport|Preveza/Lefkada]] (begins 3 May 2020), [[Pula Airport|Pula]], [[Keflav\u00edk International Airport|Reykjav\u00edk\u2013Keflav\u00edk]], [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]], [[Salzburg Airport|Salzburg]], [[Sofia Airport|Sofia]], [[Split Airport|Split]], [[Turin Airport|Turin]], [[Zakynthos Airport|Zakynthos]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Enter Air]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Sofia Airport|Sofia]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[KLM]] | [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol|Amsterdam]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Lauda (airline)|Lauda]] | [[Vienna International Airport|Vienna]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bristolpost.co.uk/news/bristol-news/lauda-new-flights-bristol-airport-3365772|title=Austrian airline Lauda has launched new cheap flights at Bristol Airport|website=bristolpost.co.uk|date=26 September 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Loganair]]<ref name=\"loganair.co.uk\">{{cite web|url=https://www.loganair.co.uk/flybmi-update-17th-february/|title=F